Class Picture

java.lang.Object
model.Picture
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Picture
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Class that implements logic of how Pictures are created, how new tags and captions for pictures are added and modified
